business_flows.name: Account Creation Flow
business_flows.description: This flow allows users to create a new PIKEPASS account, providing them access to the online services related to their toll account.
steps: Navigate to the 'Create Your Account' page.
Fill in account details including account number, driver's license number, email, username, password, and security questions.
Receive a confirmation of account creation.
success_criteria: The user receives a confirmation message and can log in with the new credentials.

business_flows.name: Account Login Flow
business_flows.description: This flow allows existing users to log into their PIKEPASS account to manage their toll activities and payments.
success_criteria: The user is successfully redirected to their account dashboard without errors.

business_flows.name: Payment Processing Flow
business_flows.description: This flow allows users to make payments towards their PIKEPASS accounts.
steps: Navigate to the 'Make A Payment' page.
Enter payment details including amount and payment method.
success_criteria: The payment is processed, and the user receives a confirmation message with transaction details.

business_flows.name: Toll Calculation Flow
business_flows.description: This flow allows users to calculate toll costs for planned trips using the toll calculator tool.
steps: Select turnpikes, entry, and exit plazas.
success_criteria: The toll cost is correctly calculated and displayed based on user inputs.

business_flows.name: Store Locator Flow
business_flows.description: This flow allows users to find PIKEPASS store locations based on their location preferences.
steps: Enter the zipcode and select city and radius.
View list of nearby PIKEPASS store locations.
success_criteria: The user is presented with accurate and relevant store location results based on their search criteria.
